king about something they saw (\"I rarely use shocking to describe a place!\") and asking where it is, but I don't have context about what they're referring to, I should ask for clarification. But they might be referring to something that was pushed to them automatically (like a travel post from 小红书 or something similar).\n\nGiven my limitations, I should ask the user to clarify or provide more context about what they're referring to - perhaps they can share an image or link, or tell me more about the source of this description."},{"type":"text","text":"[[reply_to_current]] 哈，这个\"震撼\"是哪看到的？图片、链接还是分享？给我看看才能帮你找 😄"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":0,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1776332317268}}
